      "para_id": "Q004951.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , Simat-Ištaran , his beloved sister : Adad-tillati , child of Abiya , is your servant ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q004951.10",
      "line_range": "10",
      "translation": "(ii 6) Scribe ."
    }
  ],
